+## 2026-07-17 Australia/Sydney - ADP V0.1 task ADP-S3-P03-T038 (media-lead to official-original resolver + event grouping + abstain; NOT_DEPLOYED)
+
+- Thirty-eighth task of the ADP V0.1 FINAL EXECUTION program (S3-P03). Goal: allow media to surface a discovery lead, but require every lead to resolve back to the issuing authority's official original and merge reposts, and if no official original exists, ABSTAIN (UNKNOWN) and never impersonate official. NOT_DEPLOYED, 0 recurring cloud cost; a resolver, not wired into the worker. Deliverables under arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/: tools/media_resolver.py (resolve_lead binding a lead to an official original by a cited 发文字号 or a referenced title, else ABSTAIN with the lead never claiming official; group_events merging reposts of one event into a single canonical event by the official canonical id; and resolve_all; built on the T024 identity, with a whitelisted document-number prefix so a cited number is extracted precisely rather than over-grabbing the surrounding sentence), MEDIA_RESOLVER_SPEC.md, and evidence/ADP-S3-P03-T038/media_leads_50.json. Acceptance verified (evidence/ADP-S3-P03-T038/test-results/resolver_tests.txt, ACCEPTANCE = PASS, exit 0): across 50 media leads -- 28 resolvable (20 by a cited document number and 8 by a referenced title, with reposts) plus 22 real board3 news leads with no official original -- every lead resolves as expected (50 of 50), the 28 with an original bind to it while the 22 without abstain as UNKNOWN, no lead impersonates official (0 impersonations, and every abstained lead stays media_lead not A0), and reposts of one event merge into a single canonical event (the official document doi:gov/1 has a repost_count of 4), giving 8 official-backed events and 22 abstained events. A real defect was fixed during implementation: a loose CJK prefix over-grabbed the sentence text before a document number, so the extractor switched to a whitelist of central-government document-number prefixes. Cost (unknown != 0): new_requests 0, D1 0, R2 0, model_calls 0. Ends IMPLEMENTATION_READY_FOR_INDEPENDENT_VERIFICATION.
+
 ## 2026-07-17 Australia/Sydney - ADP V0.1 task ADP-S3-P03-T037 (Board 3 eligibility gate + policy date/status extractors; NOT_DEPLOYED)
 
 - Thirty-seventh task of the ADP V0.1 FINAL EXECUTION program and the first of S3-P03 (Board 3 admission, shadow, and switch). Goal: before ranking, admit only official primary documents to Board 3 (the policy view) and exclude news noise, and identify the four policy dates 成文 (written), 发布 (published), 施行 (effective), and 失效 (expired) plus the effectiveness status. NOT_DEPLOYED, 0 recurring cloud cost; a gate and extractors, not wired into the worker ranker. Deliverables under arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/: tools/board3_gate.py (is_eligible admitting only an official A0/A1 source with a primary document type and excluding media, search, news, and interpretation; extract_dates_status producing the four dates plus status; and gate_board3; built on the T033 identity, the T034 policy dates, and the T036 classifier), BOARD3_GATE_SPEC.md, and evidence/ADP-S3-P03-T037/board3_policy_sample_200.json. Acceptance verified (evidence/ADP-S3-P03-T037/test-results/gate_tests.txt, ACCEPTANCE = PASS, exit 0): on a 200-item policy-view sample of 85 real board3 media items (news noise such as a Taiwan-Affairs-Office news item and a lifestyle piece) plus 115 synthetic official policy documents with known dates, the gate admits 115 and rejects 85, the news pollution in the admitted view is 0 of 115 which is 0.000% (required under 1%), and the key-date accuracy for 成文/发布/施行/失效 plus status on the admitted official documents is 115 of 115 which is 100% (required at least 99%). This excludes news noise from the policy view before ranking and roots out the DRIFT-FACT-006 board3 pollution. Cost (unknown != 0): new_requests 0, D1 0, R2 0, model_calls 0. Ends IMPLEMENTATION_READY_FOR_INDEPENDENT_VERIFICATION.
